        <mxCell id="xKtSK4JFK4_TB1QOGjpG-21" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Looping through the targets&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;The aim is to find geometries from QM that recreate the vibrations seen in FTIR. So here the vibrational frequencies from QM calculations are subtracted from experimental frequencies of acetone/water mixtures.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
